# Opcodes CALL + RET: callee resta 8, retorna. Exit final = 50 - 8 = 42
# Layout bytecode:
#   Decls (3*7=21B) | Call [rel] (3B) | ExitTop R (3B) | Sub R Eight R (7B) | Ret (1B)
# Post-Call offset=24, Sub offset=27, rel=3
D 0 0 R Integer 50
D 0 0 Z Integer 0
D 0 0 Eight Integer 8
R 0 0 Call [3]
R 0 0 ExitTop [R]
R 0 0 Sub [R, Eight] R
R 0 0 Ret []
